window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Being a Horseman of the Apocalypse isn't as glamorous as it sounds. </p> <p>Alan can barely hold things together himself. Now he's expected to convince a pissed off retired Archangel to once again join the fight while juggling a love life with heaven's deadliest warrior. </p> <p>Just when things don't look like they can get any worse, two more Horsemen are chosen. But instead of helping, they only complicate the matter more. One's as high as a kite, only interested in her next fix, and the other's being hoodwinked by the enemy. </p>"; 
